{"tid":587204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打機輸8千唔忿氣 口罩男劫機舖","createTime":"2018-03-10T08:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T10:38:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"28ec88cc2b0e6374ce8b95d1d488c9f5f6bd355c","tid":587204,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T08:30:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180310/20327877\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180310%2F20327877&d=7TsPuvTwDarcJYwxYOrhW10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=f03dd5fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180310%2F20327877&h=a3c10685\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180310/20327877</a><br />\n<br />\n打機輸8千唔忿氣<br />\n口罩男劫機舖<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】葵涌屏富徑3至15號地下一間遊戲機中心，昨凌晨近零時，機舖接近關門時間，只剩下一名本地男顧客，他突然走近櫃枱，向姓施68歲男職員聲稱要8千元，男職員表示「冇錢，邊有8千蚊？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該男子伸手入櫃枱，搶去約3千元紙幣，得手奪門逃去。據稱，該男子昨晚前來打機，主要玩釣魚機，「唱咗好多錢玩，玩親都輸」，估計因此打劫機舖。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場，在附近兜截沒有發現，現正翻查閉路電視錄影，追緝涉案年約25至35歲、身高約1.7米男子，案發時身穿灰色外套、深色長褲、白色運動鞋，戴眼鏡、口罩及藍色鴨舌帽。"},{"pid":"76d16ec98259e38dce903481f1b54bf2c2f7862e","tid":587204,"uid":46312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T09:00:24.000Z","msg":"願賭服輸喎<br />\n係咪take左野咋"},{"pid":"67caac7c5f53ee7a0bd7e23a6955cca3ac54a444","tid":587204,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T09:01:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樓主泛民打手冚家剷</span>"},{"pid":"95e285b0750c9c6cfa065d9498a94ccbc3fed963","tid":587204,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T10:22:56.000Z","msg":"打咩機會打左八千蚊？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打高達五蚊舖，　打千六場都。。。。。。"},{"pid":"e914d8fdf6c6b145287f48dd602d4f1170f55df6","tid":587204,"uid":46896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T10:27:24.000Z","msg":"咁唔通賭輸🐎去打劫投注站?"},{"pid":"c23a7bc437d9501eed6f1e9fb8cb0aa3b865cff3","tid":587204,"uid":58413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e914d8fdf6c6b145287f48dd602d4f1170f55df6","tid":587204,"uid":46896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T10:27:24.000Z","msg":"咁唔通賭輸🐎去打劫投注站?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T10:31:26.000Z","msg":"當年有套戲，吳震乳輸左馬。去打劫馬。會保險甲萬"},{"pid":"1b1668ef401298e81c79120a5698623d3b9c43ae","tid":587204,"uid":127123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T10:38:08.000Z","msg":"幾時先肯監管呢D另類賭場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}